Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Okay.\N>> Uhhuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you, doctor.\N>> Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes.\N>> I would like to say thank you for
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,guiding us on this life and making it a\Nlittle easier to get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is the last time I was here\NI was sitting in the audience and I
