Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,on my the next day as I was I work as a\Nflight attendant and as I'm trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,get on the plane walking back I couldn't\Nlook at people in the face because I
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,kept feeling these emotions in my heart\Nand um when I got to the hotel I
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't stop crying so I was calling\Nall the all the spiritual students to
