Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt numb like I couldn't practice all\Nthe books I read and I'm thinking do I
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,have to root do I have to read these\Nbooks all over again? I I don't I don't
