Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,suffering?\N>> All right. Just got a whole lot of stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,on there. What's number one? You're\Nexperiencing what?
