Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> The shaking.\N>> Shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,>> along with some pain.\N>> You know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> pain and shaking.\N>> Uh it's what I think it is. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah. Do you have a psychiatrist?\NI have in the past worked with a
