Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,>> She said yes or no.\N>> She doesn't have one at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,>> That's all I want to know.\N>> Uh Uhhuh.
