Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.32,1:30:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,woods the trees all know who you really\Nare.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.48,1:30:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a fact. exist. It sort of\Nenhances
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.36,1:31:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the significance of your own existence\Nbecause wherever you you walk, you shine
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.40,1:31:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,forth that light. I used to live in New\NYork City in the upper east side and I
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.12,1:31:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,had a certain way to go every day and I\Nwas in a pretty high state in those days
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.60,1:31:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and as I would walk down the street the\Ndormant down the road would start to
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.76,1:31:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,beam and they everywhere I went people\Nwould beam and you'd walk into the
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.56,1:31:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,hardware store and they would all shine\Nforth. It's because when you're in a
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.44,1:31:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,high state, you pretty much reshine that\Nenergy forth and people just feel a
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.32,1:31:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,gladness when you come up to them to the\Ndoor man. You look to the door man, he
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.56,1:31:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,just loves opening the door for you. He\Ndoesn't know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.67,1:31:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's all beyond the intellect.\NThat's the energy field that we've been
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.28,1:31:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about today. That energy field\Nuplifts and radiates forth. Yeah. So
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.36,1:32:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,people say, "What can I do to help the\Nworld?" And I say, "Just be who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.36,1:32:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just being who you are is what's\Nuplifting the world for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.12,1:32:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Without you folks here, the end of the\Nworld would just fall over into the
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.63,1:32:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,ocean, wouldn't it?"\N>> All right.
