Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.28,1:32:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,>> From Australia.\N>> Said, "Greetings and love from
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.36,1:32:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Australia." Oh, from Australia. Oh, God\Nbless us.
