Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.32,1:33:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> It's time to go.\N>> Okay. Time. Thank you again so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.44,1:33:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I I am I am truly blessed. I am truly\Nblessed by your presence. I am
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.28,1:33:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,profoundly blessed by your presence. I\Nthank you now and forever because we
